name: Saber 4
Lore: 'TIE interceptor often assigned to fly in a reserve position during battle. The bloodstripe of the 181st denotes the 10 kills scored by DS-181-4.',
Text: 'May deploy with a pilot as a ''react'' to a battle initiated against a TIE (for free if TIE is in Saber Squadron). May add 1 pilot. Immune to attrition < 4 when DS-181-4 piloting.',
